\mt1 2 Timothy
\is1 Introduction
\ip \bk The second letter of Paul ki Timutiyu\bk*, there din sulata of Ruma of time naprisu sikandin tenged of preaching rin concerning Jesus the messiah. Inhangyu of Paul si Timutiyu egpeendiyeen of kandin of not pad sikandin eggimatayan. Ne si Timutiyu, there pad sikandin of Ephesus the egpanulu of believers.
\ip Kayi of this letter, advised of Paul si Timutiyu eglig‑en so that egpakaantus sikandin egwali and eggimu of impeyimu of God kandin minsan taliware of me peg-antus and me pegsupak of duma person. Impanpanayan din again si Timutiyu concerning the bad egkeyingumaan of “keungelan and of ware karuan apulanan” su egpakareet this of people egpammineg.
\ip Labew of all, impasuman-suman of Paul si Timutiyu concerning the kandin life su so that to become parable of Timutiyu the faith of Paul, the pegpariralem din, the loving rin, the pegpabulus din, and the peg-antus din taliware of me pegbayad-bayad kandin.
